Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:03.54,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,The skies are clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:04.96,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,A day like this calls for...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.16,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:07.25,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,A mushroom-grilling party!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:09.26,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Or for short, a shroompa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:11.05,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,A shroompa! That sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:12.88,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,No meat, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,These are all types I've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.38,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Are you sure they're safe to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.17,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:22.32,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I made sure to only pick the edible ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.39,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I've perfectly memorized which \Nmushrooms in the nearby forests
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:29.01,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,are edible and which ones aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:30.94,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,They're {\i1}definitely{\i0} safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:33.70,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,You already have a bad record. \NWhy are you so confident?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:37.96,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist, I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:38.97,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Click, click.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.70,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Now, let the shroompa begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.48,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,We spread some butter on the grill \Nand toss the mushrooms on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:48.44,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Then we drizzle on some elvin, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:50.27,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:51.71,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That's all it takes to \Nmake them super tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:52.94,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Scoot, scoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.35,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:58.61,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Br...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:01.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Bring on the booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:03.06,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:05.84,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,It's not meat, but it's \Ngood in its own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:06.88,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.87,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I didn't know there were so many \Ndifferent types of mushrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:10.90,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Forests are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:12.52,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Here you go, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:18.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Man, nothing beats the combo of grilled \Nmushrooms and butter with soy sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:19.66,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:20.38,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:23.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What's this mushroom called?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:25.24,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,They're black dwarf mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:28.78,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I only picked the ones that \Nhadn't grown too big yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:28.78,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:30.19,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,And this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:31.85,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Gnome's hideaways.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.87,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,They don't grow in this area, \Nso I grow them in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:38.25,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,At their full size, they're big \Nenough for a gnome to hide under.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:38.89,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Is this the same kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:41.05,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:43.05,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,That's also a gnome's hideaway...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:45.42,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,or rather, it's a gnome-maker mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:49.73,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,It's what they call a poison mushroom. \NEating it makes you shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:49.98,Main - Top,,0,0,0,,Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:56.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Did you just say "poison"? \NDid you really just say "poison"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:59.30,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master, your smile looks scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:00.38,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:03.89,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You said they were all \N{\i1}definitely{\i0} safe to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.14,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,The ones I picked are perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.20,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,This is one I've been growing in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You think I care?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:13.86,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:15.07,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:15.62,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.67,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:17.50,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.35,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:27.60,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wh-What? What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:29.52,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.04,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama, you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.16,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Cute? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:35.48,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wait, what is this?! Don't tell me I...
