Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.38,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm totally a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.62,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,You certainly look young enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.29,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:19.09,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,But don't worry! It doesn't do any \Nharm, other than making you shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.66,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I'll find out how to turn you \Nback to normal in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.22,Narration - Top,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I hope I can change back to normal soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:32.99,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Um, Lady Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.07,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This is very difficult \Nfor me to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:36.82,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.31,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:39.56,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Scoot, scoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.73,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's not going to make me happy! \NI'm not actually a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:49.50,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Even though your body's smaller, \NI guess your soul weighs the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.62,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,What are you seeing, exactly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:57.70,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'm glad the village had clothes \Nlike yours in children's sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.20,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Here, Mama! Open wide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.82,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Again, I'm not a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:08.06,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,{\i1}Memoirs{\i0}, Volume 1: {\i1}The Intrinsic Differences \NBetween Knowledge and Experience{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:09.69,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What book is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:12.72,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,A literary masterpiece about \Nintuitive cognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:16.34,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's not a book you'd read to \Na child. Not that I'm a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.69,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Listening to it will make you sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.85,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It's great for getting babies to nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:26.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.49,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,A kids' lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:32.53,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I tried making it fancy \Nto suit your appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.89,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're enjoying this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.24,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Where's Halkara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:38.81,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,She's secluded herself in her room to \Nsearch for a way to turn you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.26,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,She'd better find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:44.34,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Um, Lady Azusa... I have a favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.01,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Floaty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.97,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Would you let me pet your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:53.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,At this point, you might as \Nwell coddle me all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I've resigned myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.29,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pet, pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.98,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, you're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:04.50,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Even your grumpy face is adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.60,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,Hey! No fair getting her to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.24,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pet, pet, pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:09.87,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,I'm petting you more gently \Nthan she did, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.20,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,My petting is much softer \Nthan hers, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.70,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,That is not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:13.70,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Pet, pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.69,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I can pet her more gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:18.09,Main,Flatorte,0,0,0,,It's obvious that my way feels nicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:23.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Are you fighting or petting me? \NMake up your minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:27.49,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Nope, I can't reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.07,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Here you go, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.11,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Thanks, Rosalie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:35.67,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Hey, Sister... if you want, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.81,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,I could comb your hair for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.20,0:06:41.07,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.48,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,Hmm... It's a very distant memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:47.45,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,but I think I played with dolls this way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:50.48,Main,Rosalie,0,0,0,,back when I lived in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.52,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.27,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Sorry I took so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.63,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, did you find a clue \Nto changing me back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:58.62,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.90,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I found nothing! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then why did you look \Npleased with yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:10.00,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,I decided to tell you the truth and \Napologize, and this is what my face did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.48,Main,Halkara,0,0,0,,All I can do is sincerely apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:14.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This doesn't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to ask the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:22.02,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Vosanosanon ujishidau veyani enrila!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.61,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,That was a nice bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You've gotten used to appearing \Nin the bathtub, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.27,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Oh? Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:32.08,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You bear an uncanny resemblance to Azusa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:33.00,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Shoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:33.96,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Could you be her daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:34.45,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Shoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's me. I'm Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I shrank because of a poison mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.53,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,How cute! How adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:47.33,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Resisting being treated like a \Nchild makes you even cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:52.77,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I see. So you decided to rely on \Nthe knowledge of the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:56.89,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Please do something! \NI can't stay like this forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.83,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:02.64,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Would it not be nice to live as the \Nmost adorable child there is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:06.97,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll tell everyone the great \Ndemon Beelzebub lost to a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.52,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:12.82,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll search Vanzeld \NCastle for a way to restore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.82,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You'll need to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:18.33,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,We'll bring Shalsha and Falfa, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.19,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:20.90,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:38.94,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Ah, that was just like being in Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:40.75,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,What an explosion of cuteness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:44.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Um, please don't tell \NPecora about this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:48.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If she finds out, \Nit'll complicate things for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.90,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Greetings, Dear Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:51.82,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:56.03,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I can't have you underestimating \Nthe Demon King's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:58.97,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:01.66,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I never dreamed you could look \Nso adorable, Dear Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.85,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I want to go back to normal, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.56,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Oh, what a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.83,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You should, at least, stay like \Nthis until I get tired of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:09.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Pecora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.55,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Then let's ask the members of your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:13.74,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Scoot, scoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:16.68,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Falfa and Shalsha, do you prefer \Nyour mama as she is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.67,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,or do you want her the way she was before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.30,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,If you choose "as she is now," \NI'll give you all the candy you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.05,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Um, what should we say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.45,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,The ultimate decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:28.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Don't be bought off with candy! \NMama wants to go back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:30.15,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.58,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,All right, enough with the jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:33.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.60,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Fwip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:37.29,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Allow me to suggest a way you \Ncan change back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:42.70,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Within the demon realm, in a forest \Nfar, far away from the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.31,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,there is a massive tree \Nknown as the World Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:51.66,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,At its very top is a pharmacist who \Ndeals in every medicine ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.06,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,The World Tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:55.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,We have to go that far to fix this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.55,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Slow and steady wins the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:10:00.61,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,It's better than trying some shady \Ntreatment method, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:04.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All right. I'll try climbing \Nup this World Tree, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.68,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What's the place like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.32,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,The inside of the World Tree is hollow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.37,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,and it's laid out like a complex maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.13,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,The top is the 108th floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:16.73,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,and on the way there are many areas \Ninhabited by ferocious wild animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:19.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,A dungeon with 108 floors is pretty big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:21.99,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But still, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:26.03,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,In that case, Vania, please take \NDear Sister to the World Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:30.43,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,So I really have to go, then? \NI suppose I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:33.71,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Sending my younger sister alone \Nworries me. I will go, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:38.65,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,By the way, Beelzebub, you have plenty of \Nwork to catch up on while they're away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.55,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.09,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Gloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.85,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.02,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I want to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:48.70,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It might be dangerous. \NYou two need to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.29,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:52.44,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I know Mother will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.03,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:57.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let's get going, Fatla, Vania!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:03.12,Eyecatch,Title,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,335)}I've Been Killing {\c&HE4AE06&}Slimes\N{\c&H313536&}for {\c&HE4AE06&}300 Years {\c&H313536&}and\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Maxed Out {\c&H313536&\3c&HFFFFFF&}My {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.75,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(486,1)\bord0}World Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:05.74,Main - Top,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:08.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Its size is pretty shocking \Nwhen I see it in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:11.23,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,I haven't seen the World Tree in some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.99,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Since that school field trip, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:15.82,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I came here for a field trip, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow, you've both been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.27,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Even if it's a complex, mysterious dungeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:26.74,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm doing this to go back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.78,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'll get through it, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.40,sign_16557_234_Elevator_to_10th,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1484,1)}Elevator to 10th floor just over there! \N1300 Coyns
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.64,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Coyns are demon currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Not that. The elevator part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.72,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Many people want to go higher \Nand higher up the World Tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.22,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,which led to the sale of elevator usage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.92,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,The higher you want to \Ngo, the more it costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:54.48,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be more like a dungeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.94,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,It does have aspects of one, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:59.74,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,The 11th and 12th floors are home to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:04.12,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,wild World Tree 11th Floor Wolves \Nand World Tree 12th Floor Wolves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.53,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,so we'll need to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.84,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What a dumb way to name animal species...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:09.26,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wait, where's Vania?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.61,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.53,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I went to buy deep-fried \Nbuns from that shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.83,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,The deep-fried buns here are so \Nexquisite, they've become famous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.27,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is just a tourist trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.18,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That smells good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let me try a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:25.50,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Good thing they gave you the \Nchildren's price, isn't it, Azusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.99,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,Floor 1 → Floor 10
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.99,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Step, step, step, step...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:32.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,There's a lot I'd like to say here, \Nbut let's head to floor 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:33.99,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,We've got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:38.01,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,They want 500 coyns per person \Nfor wild animal conservation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:43.24,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Incidentally, the 13th floor also has \Na gate where you'll need to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.52,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This seems like such a shoddy business...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.77,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(439,1)\bord0}Floor 11: Jungle Area
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:50.28,Main - Top,Azusa,0,0,0,,This definitely looks like a place \Nwhere scary animals would live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.63,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,They're totally tame! \NWhere are the wild animals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:12.20,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Many visitors here are powerful demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.93,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,so the animals are no longer hostile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:18.09,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,In fact, they learned to bow \Ntheir heads to beg for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.59,sign_16557_234_Elevator_to_10th,Text,0,0,0,,{\move(320,300,320,285,1775,2024)}Elevator to the 17th floor this way\N{\1a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\t(1733,1816,1 \1a&H00&\4a&HBB&)}2200 coyns per adult
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:21.59,Main - Top,Azusa,0,0,0,,Suddenly it costs more \Nto make less progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:25.55,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,On the 18th floor, we can see \NWorld Tree 18th Floor Wildcats
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:26.13,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:28.47,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,and a rare plant called the \NWorld Tree 18th Floor Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:27.86,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Rose, rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.96,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,And I bet there's another elevator \Non the 19th floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:35.11,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Yes. I believe the fare is 3,000 coyns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:40.11,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs30\q2\c&HF3F3F3&\shad2\4a&HAA&\pos(315,55)}~ Floor 19
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:40.11,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs30\q2\c&HF3F3F3&\shad2\4a&HAA&\pos(315,130)}~ Floor 17
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:40.11,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs30\q2\c&HF3F3F3&\shad2\4a&HAA&\pos(295,205)}Floors 1~10
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.10,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's demonic business! \NThey really are demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.18,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.86,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,When I came here on my field trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:46.66,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I tried to see how far I \Ncould get without paying,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:50.21,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,but I got lost and ended up \Nlate to our meet-up time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:53.70,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Life in this area relies \Non the tourist industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.67,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,so the maze here is more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:58.90,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,They dig holes, add poisonous \Nswamps, and other things
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.30,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,to make sure visitors \Nwill use the elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,They're building a dungeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.93,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,Floor 11 → Floor 18
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:04.92,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Step, step, step...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.05,Main,Roses,0,0,0,,Rose, rose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.97,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,Floor 19 → Floor 38
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:10.97,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Step, step, step...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:13.97,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,It's getting late. \NLet's stay here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.80,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Ka-tunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.20,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,This feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.49,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's nothing like the \NWorld Tree I had imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:25.76,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Yes, there was no stopping its \Ntransition to a tourist stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.46,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,That said, there are no elevators \Nafter the eighth station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.85,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What is this, Mount Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:34.45,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Azusa, it might be a strange \Nway to bring this up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.51,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Thank you for giving me this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:42.56,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,It had been a long time since my \Nsister and I took a trip together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:47.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bet. You're both so busy with \Nwork, I'm sure you never had time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:51.07,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,I must apologize. This is \Npart of our work, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:54.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's fine. Sorry for dragging you \Nboth into such a weird task.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:58.40,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Well, the floors will be more \Ncramped from this point on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.64,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,so we'll be moving upward at a faster pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:03.93,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Tomorrow night, we'll \Nlodge on the 84th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.19,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,After that, it's a real \Ndungeon, with no lodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.71,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Right! Let's do this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.08,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,Floor 38 → Floor 39
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:11.08,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Step, step, step...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.33,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,Floor 39 → Floor 85
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.79,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:31.84,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,This floor is home to drooling \Nsloths and snot-nosed sloths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.76,Main,Sloth,0,0,0,,Durr!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.90,Main,Sloth,0,0,0,,Durr!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.55,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,They are ferocious, so they will attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.51,Main,Sloth,0,0,0,,Durr!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:41.61,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Kiddie Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.61,Main,Sloth,0,0,0,,Durr!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:45.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,As far as my stats go, I still \Nseem to be doing pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.27,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Wow! That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.86,Main,Sloths,0,0,0,,Durr!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.27,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,You can leave these to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:54.52,Main,Sloths,0,0,0,,Durr!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:56.80,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You two are pretty strong, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.16,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess you are Leviathans, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:58.78,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.32,Main,Sloths,0,0,0,,Durr!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.30,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Now, let us hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.05,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\bord0}Floor 89
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:06.21,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\bord0}Floor 96
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.22,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\bord0}Floor 102
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.59,sign_17847_255_Floor_1_____Floo,Text,0,0,0,,Floor 87 → Floor 107
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:13.10,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\bord0}Floor 107
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:13.10,Main - Top,Azusa,0,0,0,,We made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.54,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.09,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,I knew what you were going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.16,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,We've come this far together, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:35.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:40.74,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,What's this? I feel kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:43.46,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I'm not normally the type to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.38,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,You mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.70,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,We're still on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:50.63,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,When we were still children,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:54.05,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,you nearly jumped off and fell \Nfrom here, didn't you, Vania?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.75,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything that clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:17:01.93,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,You were the one who just started \Ncomplaining more as we kept going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:07.52,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,And then Father said we never \Nshould have brought you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:11.55,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Well, climbing that volcano \Nreally was exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.45,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,And it took longer than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:18.07,Main,Vania,0,0,0,,As I always tell you, not everything \Nworks out exactly as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:21.02,Main,Fatla,0,0,0,,Or maybe you're just too lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.84,Locales,Text,0,0,0,,{\bord0}Floor 108
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:39.18,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I ate a gnome-maker mushroom \Nand became smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:42.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Do you have any medicine that \Ncan change me back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.86,Main,Pharmacist,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:47.21,Main,Pharmacist,0,0,0,,Until recently, that mushroom's \Neffects were difficult to treat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:50.35,Main,Pharmacist,0,0,0,,but I've since learned that a certain \Nmedicine works well against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:52.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.53,Main,Pharmacist,0,0,0,,Yes, it's become a huge hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.37,Main,Pharmacist,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.74,Main,Pharmacist,0,0,0,,It's made by a witch named Eno who's \Nwell-known as the Witch of the Cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:03.95,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:07.63,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,Hello! It's the Witch of the Cave, Eno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:10.75,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,I brought three more \Ncases of that medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:11.46,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Eno!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.21,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,Huh? Whose child are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.71,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,Wait, are you... the Witch \Nof the Highlands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:23.84,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,Wow! You actually walked \Nall the way up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:24.60,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:29.04,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,Dragons can't make it, but wyverns \Ncan come straight to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.60,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,They carry medicines and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.79,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,Also, it doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:36.37,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,I deliver Mandragora Pills \Nto Vanzeld Castle, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:40.14,Main,Eno,0,0,0,,I'm certain the Demon King \Nknows I transport them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:40.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:44.64,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I forgot that a wyvern could \Nfly straight to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.94,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Oopsie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:46.78,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Tee-hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:50.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No, you totally knew. And you \Nknew about the medicine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.00,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.47,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:57.96,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,We were allowed to ride a wyvern \Nback to get here faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:00.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I just want to take that \Nmedicine and have a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.52,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm a mess after that crazy adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.01,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:07.98,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,You might as well return to \Nnormal in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.14,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, we did work hard to get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.03,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Maybe that would be more moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:16.69,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,Really? It was just Mandragora Pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.51,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,You worked so hard for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All's well that ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm going back to normal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.20,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:32.49,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I'm apprehensive about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.58,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,If she gets bigger,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:39.38,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,she won't fit in children's clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:44.10,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Oh, Dear Sister! How scandalous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.10,0:19:46.10,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,As your little sister, \NI can't bear to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.28,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Pecora! You knew this would \Nhappen and didn't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:52.93,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I don't know what you\Nmean. I haven't the foggiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:56.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,At this point, we all might \Nas well take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:59.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,We'll all be naked together, \Nincluding you! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:00.90,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:06.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,There's nothing better than a big bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.54,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:12.59,Main,Beelzebub,0,0,0,,It hits even deeper when \Nyou're exhausted from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.22,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Pecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:18.71,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,D-Dear Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:22.98,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Does being in the bath with \Nall of us embarrass you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:28.60,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,N-No, it's just... I-I'm not \Nused to this sort of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:31.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Since you're the Demon King,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.60,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess you wouldn't take \Nbaths with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But when you get me, I get you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:40.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get a good look at you naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.61,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Th-That's scandalous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:46.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Being naked is the proper \Nattire for a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:49.88,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Besides, it's not embarrassing when \Neveryone's in it together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:54.97,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Still, you took your joke a \Nlittle too far this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Listen, Pecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:01.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No matter what your reason is, \NI'm your older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,and if my little sister does \Nsomething bad, I'll scold her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.11,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.94,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.39,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.50,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No more hard feelings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:19.02,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Um, Dear Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:19.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:25.91,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I always dreamed of getting a kiss \Nbecause of the books I read,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:30.13,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,but nothing beyond that was \Nwritten in the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:33.71,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Ah. So that's the most \Nyou could imagine, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:34.91,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're very pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:38.76,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,So there's something I'd \Nlike you to do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Just name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:44.94,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,May I... touch your breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What?! What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.52,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I thought I should get used to it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:52.59,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,I hoped touching your chest \Nwould get me more accustomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:54.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That is {\i1}not{\i0} allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:58.34,Main,Pecora,0,0,0,,Why isn't it allowed, Dear Sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:02.19,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If the Demon King had some weird awakening, \Nit'd cause irreversible damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:03.96,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I can't grant that favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:06.20,Main - Top,Pecora,0,0,0,,Dear Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:11.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,For the sake of world peace, \Nyou need to remain pure!
